data.text: Considering myself exceedingly lucky. Aside from sleeping the entire weekend, the side effects I experienced were minimal. My friend who received their 2nd vaccine the same day had a horrible weekend & is still miserable. So, hope for the best but expect the worst
22 hours later: sore arm, fatigue, wooziness. No appetite. Drinking lots of water & catching up on my to read list
@EppSally THANKS!  I’m taking today, tomorrow, & Monday off, just in case. So far, I’ve drank lots of water, napped, read, & tweeted. I adlore the idea of my immune system flashing into action!!!!
@Tealan Get lots of sleep tonight so your immune system can flash into action. It’s soooo great that you’ve had dose 2!!!!
Adding woozy to the list of fun post-vaccination effects. There shall be cake & bubbly NEXT weekend
Been 6 hours. No superpowers. yet. Only a sore arm & fatigue. Yet
It didn’t hurt! We cheered. Thank you to all the volunteers to made this happen. #gratitude #vaccinated #vaccination https://t.co/vcj39po4qx

Dressing for comfort. No gown & tiara. Glamming it up by wearing blue eyeliner to match my mermaid socks. Thought of wearing glitter powder but thought if I sparkle, they'll take me in for turning into a vampire.
